PREVIEW ONLY — DO NOT DEPLOY THIS FILE.

miami-page-preview.html is a single-file copy of the Miami page with all
images embedded as base64 so it opens anywhere without the assets folder.
It is ~635KB and would hurt page speed / Core Web Vitals if published.

To view: double-click miami-page-preview.html.
To deploy: use /car-shipping-miami-fl.html in the parent folder instead.
